despite peoples claims for it being a pay2win game youd be terribly mistaken all frames are obtainable through regular play you can choose to invest real money if you so wish to get the frames you wish or you may choose to get it as you would with any other game its not a mmo more of a 4player coop third person action game allowing you to take control of a warframe refered too as tenno the race controlling it basically youre a space ninja you get to zip line run along walls back flip walls slash a big  sword and generally kick  there are three factions corpus grineer and infested infested the infested are mostly melee based with strange aliencorrupted creatures that can inflict deadly poisons or maul you to death corpus the corpus are like the evil science type guys these have moa robots practically guns with legs they mostly use lazer weapons not only that there are melee corpus who make use of electric prods nasty as well as the annoying shield spray robots which can repair the shields of foes around it grineer the grineer unlike the corpus have more standard type weapons less futuristic they also have melee uses who try to slice you youll find them doing a lot of damage if they successfully land a hit originally this game had started off as something so very small with only a few frames loki excalibur volt rhino and mag it slowly started growing and becoming so much more really basic levels and basic movement and have strongly benefitted from constant player feedback improving the game with every update the game is extremely responsive however be prepared to get a hand ache after hours of play with how much you need to keep moving to avoid enemies and help allies one minor issue for me is that this game lacks any cover mechanic enemies can cover but you are unable to blocking is in the game but it also feels rather pointless since ive found myself in little to no situations where it was actually neccesary or helpful it is also assigned by default to mouse button 4 if youre old fashioned like me and have a mouse with only 3 buttons you may need to assign it to a spot on your keyboard the game is simple the graphics amazing it works on my really substandard pc with a graphics card as basic as an asus eah6450 with a simple godawful amd athlon 64 processor 3200 199 ghz and 300gb of ram running winxp sp3 yes this pc is about as old as the hills you may not be able to play with friends with a pc like this but you sure as hell can play the game at well over 30fps and as far as im concerned that is absolutely astonishing considering many other games with worse graphics than this run about as fast as a snale on salt do i recommend this game hell yes i would recommend it to everyone even if you wouldnt like it try it anyway since its free to play and you really just cant complain ive had more hours out of this beauty than i have out of any aaa $6000 piece of over hyped trash
