recommended
warframe is an action game in which you control a warframe a robot ninjaesque character with a specific set of 4 abilities that are unique to that warframe at the time of writing there are 22 warframes to choose from but you have a limited amount of slots to keep these warframes in unfortunately to unlock more slots you have to play real world money but provided you have a job you do have a job right you wont go bankrupt from this there are multiple types of missions ranging from assassinations to exterminations to mobile defense you can play solo or with up to 3 other people and you can drop in or drop out at any time playing warframe with a group of friends is seriously some of the most fun you will have in a free to play game but playing solo isnt that great luckily if you have no friends you can join random people online so you never have to worry about going solo unless you want to but why would you everything in warframe requires resources which can be obtained from different planets if you want one resource in particular youll have to go to a planet that contains that resource because they differ from planet to planet in order to get parts to get a new warframe however youll have to farm the boss of the planet and while it can be a chore it is alleviated a little bit if youre farming with friends or at least with other people for a free to play game warframe has a lot of content and a pretty fair market system the only thing you have to pay money for are cosmetics and have no effect on the game whatsoever everything else can be obtained for free in conclusion warframe is a very fun free to play game that increases exponentially in value if you have some friends with you while it can be a grind sometimes and a little repetitive this game is definitely worth your time and if you can grab some friends youll probably lose some sleep playing this game and hey its free so what do you have to lose download warframe and try it out you wont be dissapointed gameplay 45