warframe is a tactical third person shooter set in a vast and continually expanding universe that is very interesting if you look into its lore the game is set on your character an old tenno warrior who is in an massive suit of armour called a warframe a warframe is a suit of armour that was placed onto a tenno when they are initaited and has 4 special abilities and a wide array of advantages such as better shields or armour you a lone tenno was put into cyrosleep after a great war beetween the sentients and the as i call them the orokin people you wake up centuries later to a unverse filled with corruption greed and violence and it is up to you and your fellow tenno to restore peace once more to the solar system gameplay wise the game is built around you doing acrobatics and maneuvers to outsmart your enemies such as running across a wall to reach an enemy with your shotgun as you progress through the game youll find things called mods these mods are used to augment your warframe and weapons to certain advantages one example of this is to give a rocket launcher a faster fire rate or a shotgun more accuracy whilst the mods do little to improve your items when you first get them you can upgrade them with fusion cores or with other duplicates of mods you can say get a damage mod from the basic %20 increase to a phenominal %200 increase on the max rank this system works beutifully and works well with the whole concept of you being your own unique character the classes in his game are set in what type of warframe you have there are over 20 warframes currently in the game the most recent being mesa and with each one comes a different experience your warframe is unique with the abilities and attributes it has one example is the warframe rhino a beast of a warframe that has high armour shields and health and a powerful array of abilites that revolve around either taking or dealing damage each of your warframes comes with 4 revive tokens which replenish every day to the maximun of 4 this is very useful as solo players will find killing enemies difficult on higher levels apart from your warframe you will have access to a wide array of primary secondry and melee weapons each catagory has a subclass which include handcannons staffs longswords rifles and many more some of these subclasess require different types of mods such as a well modded rifle set will not work on a shotgun as they are two different weapons types same as your warframe you can mod your weapons with a wide array of mods that include increasing damage to mods that inflict elemental damage or status effects there is alot of things that i can talk about but there is just too much to fit in a review this game is free and does not force you to pay and it is fairly easy to farm for resouces and build that all important weapon youve been wanting this feels satisfying and well achieved and one of the many reasons why a have played warframe for over a year yes i realise it says i have less than an hour of gametime but i have over 1000 hours on the browser version of the game i give this game a 455 a very well earned score keep up the great work de d
