ing and rng then youll end up buying stuff in market which is expensive i mean one weapon can cost you up to 250 platinums or about 15usd now its up to you what and how you want new stuff in this game by grinding or by paying overall this game is highly addicting stuff that effects gameplay is free and sparkly stuff will cost you money developers have to make money too right rng can be a pain in the behind but with the help of friends and clan mates this issue can be resolved new stuff that developers have planned for future major updates is extremely awesome overall i highly recommend this game
