warframe is the best free2play game i have ever played not only is it a fun game that is constantly getting new content and features as it is in open beta right now but it is the best free2play model i have ever seen in a game like most f2p games it has an in game earned moneytype credits and a paid for type platinum in warframe every single item can be obtained without spending platinum the only exception to this is vanity items and room for more warframes and weapons but you can actually earn platinum to buy those things through the trading system if you have something rare you can trade it to other people in exchange for platinum the developers also have a very active role in the community they have livestreams every week and are active on the games forums instead of seeing the developers as more of an atm for games than anything else ea for example you see them as people who actually want to make a great game overall this is a fantastic system and has actually encouraged me to spend money on the game not because i have to in order to do well in it but because i want to support the growth of this fantastic game
