you are a tenno an ancient warrior reawakened to a solar system in conflict the grineer a genetically deteriorated empire who use cloning fighting against the corpus a merchant cult with strong technology and weapons there is also the infested thrown in for good measure who through a sentient virus morphs living and robotic beings into hideous monstrosities warframe plays somewhat similar to left4dead you can go coop with up to four people starting off at one part of a randomly generated map and make your way through to fulfill a objective which can be exterminating all enemies defending a point defeating a boss or other such things and afterwards you reach the exit and finish the mission warframes are exoskeletons used by players they have unique looks stats and have 4 unique abilities each when you start off you only get to choose one of three but as you progress you can craft more to use there is also a wide range of weapons there are three different kinds you have equipped primary secondary melee these can include anything from your simple rifles shotguns handguns but can also include flamethrowers throwing knives bows and many other exotic weapons which you can craft you also level up your warframe and weapons which increases stats slightly and increases mod capacity mods are a very interesting mechanic to the game they modify your warframe and weapons and let you essentially minmax what you want it adds strategy to how you play the game then there is the important question that comes up with most f2p games is this pay to win can you only have fun or be as good as other people if you pay warframe is actually surprisingly fair with its microtransactions yes you can buy warframes or weapons on the market with actual cash but its very easy to just craft your own stuff during missions you get resources and blueprint drops which you use to craft stuff the only stuff you cant actually craft is cosmetic stuff and slots to carry more warframes and weapons but thankfully you can trade with other players for platinum which you can then use so you can very easily have a great time with warframe without needing spend a single cent
