thing which dissapoints me as a warframe player 5buying platinumingame currency somehow expensive and you will feel ripped of   like for 20$ you can get like 175 plat  if you want to buy a weapone from market or a ready crafted frame it will cost you 225  plat  2 inventory slots cost 12 plat  1 warframe slot will cost 20  so you will need to spend a lot for little upgrades in the game one last note  despite of the negative side of this game  i totally recommend this game  its a great experience and you will enjoy it besides its still beta so bugs will be fixed soon  i will wait for you in the field fellow tenno 
