se this cannot be done by looking at the engine and server for now this one will only for the new players the missions and tutorial can be quite confusing it is totally not a good time to start off playing this game right now as there are bunches of new things added to this game just remember do not rely on your primary weapon too much check and try out all your abilities every weapon you can obtain find your favorite set up and play this is my opinion it may not mean a lot but this is the comment i have on this game after playing for a year happy hunting tenno
