ed its 100% free _______________________________________________________________________________ 4 dojos one of the best perks to owning a clan is building your own dojo now like i said in the above technically speaking it is free for the lack of time and materials you will have to farm for to do this however once you own your clan and start to build your own dojo you have the freedom to make it as big as you want with no extra cost in real money currency all it takes is the time youre willing to put into it _______________________________________________________________________________ the above were my favorite points to the game in which i have added explanations the rest ill just leave as points _______________________________________________________________________________ 5 there is a multitude of weapons warframes accessories to choose from _______________________________________________________________________________ 6 different planets with missions set at different levels enemies do not level with you _______________________________________________________________________________ 7 constant updates and hotfixes to the game de has done well to keep the players in the loop as well keep good customer service _______________________________________________________________________________ 8 freedom of movement this game has one of the best parkour systems ive found yet in a video game behind assassins creed that is _______________________________________________________________________________ 9 very smooth 3rd person shooting action with the mixture of smart movement you have the ability to lunge forward and shoot slide and shoot wall run and shoot slide and slice jump and slice or slam and wall run and slice _______________________________________________________________________________ 10 the community is an alright one obviously each have their fair share of trolls within the game on warframes region chat however most questions are answered and if not in game always on the forums in a timely manner as well with an active wiki _______________________________________________________________________________ 11  _______________________________________________________________________________ cons i am not awake enough to continue thinking on this review so in time i will come back with more information
