first of all im not a fan of these kinda mmos grinding and typical slow lockon spelloncooldown gameplayi like mmorpgs though but warframe is quite different and unique the core gameplay is very dynamic fast paced action combining 3rd person shooter melee fighting and magiclike abilities everything is realtime fast and requires some skill from a player you go on various missions in up to 4 player teams to combat hordes of enemies that can rise in numbers and levels quickly providing you as much challenge as you can take the movement in this game is also great you can do many trick jumps run on wals and almost fly around if you know what you are doing there is even stealth which is fun and useful if you want to play solo now the addictive part is of course acquiring new weapons classes warframes and rare mods that augument weapons and warframes and believe me there are so many things to get and to level up some are hidden quite deep there is quite a lot of grinding but the process itself fun because the challenge escalates fast the game is honest free2play and you can unlock everything but if you want to keep everything you will have to buy inventory slots with platinum which is bought for real money or traded for rare mods between players so you dont really need to spend a dime if you are willing to grind the downside it doesnt have a huge overworld that you can walk around and explore like most other mmos just individual missions some things are still being polished and improved needs more variety in environments and missions the game is mostly pve focused there is pvp but its still in ongoing development overall its a great game for everyone who loves action intense horde combat and mmoarpg levelling and farming for loot gameplay 10 graphics 10 conclave 8 dojo 9 updates 10 grinding 10 farming 10 replayability 9 story i came to kill stuff for free overall score 98 matthew olls
