 so much more than you can give then is when youll fall out of love right away and realize that all those work are for a relationship that you will be soon leaving if you wanna make a serious longterm relationship with someone go on warframe is the one to be with but if youre the type who gets bored easily by doing the exact same thing for no real purpose find someone else to love i still recommend her though because she at least does her best to give you the fun you deserve
