a very fun free 3rd person scifi action shooter it tends to be fast paced due to the parkour styled movement system similar to mass effect 3s coop multiplayer the difference is mainly in the diverse unique weapons many warframes classes you can choose from and the fast paced parkour movement in the game now the different warframes range from classes which offer a variety style of play whether it be pure damage defense stealth tanking healing crowd control or utility we have warframes that harness  electricity fire wind water ice magnetics antimatter illusions poison sound waves the undead chaos rage based melee fury blades like true ninjas there is so much to choose from and have fun with as far as weapons go this game has some amazing weapons there are hundred of weapons to choose from you can have equipped a primary weapon secondary weapon and a melee weapon you can also unequip primary and secondary weapons and run around in a melee spree deflecting bullets at the same time with your blade weapons range from weapons that shoot ssw blades multishot missile launchers weapons that impale enemies to walls bows that are capable of killing multiple enemies with a single arrow infested rifles that fire electricity toxin launchers kitanas toxic axes that eat through armor greatswords laser rifles and machine guns it is one of my favorite games with that said however it can be grindy and a bit hard to pick up for new players with update 14 coming out it is a bit easier for new players now there is a prologue to help players through the different controls to this game while completing a quest to help ease them into the game while acquiring some beginning mods easily to help increase the damage survivability and many other things of weapons and your warframes the player community and developers are very friendly and release weekly new content along with patches and hot fixes for bugs regularly they are pretty on top of things and keep in mind this game is in the open beta stage which allows the developers to release new content constantly expanding and improving the game allowing the playerbase to evolve with the game itself i would recommend seriously trying this game for a good 1520 hours it is alot of fun and there is not game that is truly like it it is unique and most importantly play with a friendfriends it makes it that much more enjoyable enjoy
