r you but paying 5$ for my first 12 months of playing is quite acceptable ^^ aaaand if you really dont want to pay a dollar you can theres a trade system in the game allowing you to sell good parts for platinum to give you an idea 2 good mods which you can get from 510 hours in the game or less if youre rushing for it will give you about 1 potato after that how to get better frame  weapons you can clear all the planatary systems to get the basic warframes which some are insanely good just kill the boss of every planet about 5 times and youll have all the frammeeees d youll get youre 1st frame about 10h in the game then the crafting will take 3 days and a half you gotta take a day off  then personnaly ive got my 3th to 6th frame in the same day which then means after 2 weeks in the game you can have access to half the frames d but then youce got all that gear but none is really powerfull how comes you have to level up yor mods too some will be easy to level up but some costs up to a million credits so if youre tired of farming gear go get some more credits the void missons are perfect for that and you want a bonus on top of fast credits ok the void gives you some special gear too then you got your weapon lvl 30 with a potato and with good mods in it can you get it better yes theres a system called forma it gets your gear to lvl 0 but changes 1 mod slot to make it cost 50% less points 
